ZH: 我老是迟到。
EN: I am always late.
ZH: 她老是忘记带钥匙。
EN: She always forgets to bring her keys.
ZH: 他老是抱怨工作太累。
EN: He is always complaining about how tiring his job is.
ZH: 我们老是在这个咖啡店碰面。
EN: We always meet at this coffee shop.
ZH: 小狗老是在沙发上睡觉。
EN: The puppy is always sleeping on the couch.
ZH: 他们老是一起做作业。
EN: They always do homework together.
ZH: 我老是被朋友们拉去购物。
EN: I am always being dragged shopping by my friends.
ZH: 孩子们老是在公园里玩耍。
EN: The kids are always playing in the park.
ZH: 我老是在这家餐馆吃午餐。
EN: I always have lunch at this restaurant.
ZH: 她老是在网络上浏览时尚网站。
EN: She is always browsing fashion websites online.
ZH: 我们老是在周末去爬山。
EN: We always go hiking on weekends.
ZH: 妈妈老是在家做家务。
EN: Mom is always doing housework at home.
ZH: 他老是忘记锁门。
EN: He always forgets to lock the door.
ZH: 我老是在车上睡着。
EN: I always fall asleep in the car.
